spanGrp.span: How our people differ from them?
Our people are more social then they.
The different way of dressing up and the way of treatment.
Our people are much more better in everything.
nu va vse ärištädä bizım halh onnar üstünä šei
There is a huge difference between them and our people.
onnar bizimkiinän onnarın arasında ekkä dağ var nu
They came here from the mountains.
Our people were raised differently from them but we try to get along well with them.
bizım halhın vabše özgä nu no staratsa ederıh ki yola gidäh nu
Well or badly we get along with this nation but with our people we go to the church.
näblem ištem ei köti uirıh bu millätınän no bizım halhınan an kissäya gidirıh
Our people are Christian Orthodox but they are not.
They don’t come to our churches, they don’t have any relations with us.
bizım kissäya gälmerlär bizınän sviazläri yohtur
Well, so they are different from us.
